title: Chris Sullivan
itunes:title: Chris Sullivan
itunes:subtitle: CHRIS SULLIVAN (This is Us, The Knick, Stranger Things, Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2) joins Anna to discuss murder, breakfast burritos, Swingers, Isaac Lamb and his proposal video, Mount St. Helens, The Situation and a bad date. Anna and Chris then give
description:
